				..controls (443.179993,527.565979) and (452.363007,508.570007)..(441.718994,492.449005)
				--(440.421997,490.488007)--(444.281006,489.976990)..controls (463.234009,487.460999) and (471.054993,464.011993)..(457.199005,451.238007)
